[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/game/stasis_pod.gd" id="1_pod"]

; Placeholder pod built from boxes. LoganDevz's CD_Cryo_v2.blend is the intended model —
; swapping it in means replacing the Shell/Base meshes and keeping the collider and script,
; but the .blend and its scratch scene still live at the repo root, so moving them needs
; coordinating first (see TODO 12c).
;
; Same shape as RepairPanel: Node3D root with the Interactable script, collider on a child.

